Check VMware Compatibility Guide for Hitachi G400 (VSP G400) for supported SATP/PSP Plugin

https://www.vmware.com/resources/compatibility/detail.php?deviceCategory=san&productid=39102&deviceCategory=san&details=1&partner=42&keyword=400&isSVA=0&page=1&display_interval=10&sortColumn=Partner&sortOrder=Asc

Unmounting a LUN or detaching a datastore/storage device

http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?language=en_US&cmd=displayKC&externalId=2004605

Enabling the SSD option on SSD based disks/LUNS that are not detected by default

http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?language=en_US&cmd=displayKC&externalId=2013188

Example of claim rule: 
[root@esxiHost:~] esxcli storage nmp satp rule add --satp=VMW_SATP_DEFAULT_AA --device naa.60060e80122779005040277900000064 --option "enable_ssd"
